{"tid":1817412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沒投票權的香港人！杜汶澤錄45秒片：台灣你知道幸福嗎？","createTime":"2020-01-09T05:23:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T05:32:58.000Z","uid":337052,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1fb0f3df69412a661cd17c76dc01969b942e5ab8","tid":1817412,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:23:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>沒投票權的香港人！杜汶澤錄45秒片：台灣你知道幸福嗎？</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://三立新聞網SETN.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%B8%89%E7%AB%8B%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E7%B6%B2SETN.com&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF0wpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=3e0132b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">三立新聞網SETN.com</a><br />\n<br />\n2020/01/09 10:14:00<br />\n<br />\n娛樂中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n後天就是2020總統大選，各候選人紛紛進入最後衝刺的狀態，日前總統蔡英文的支持者也幫她推出新的影片協助催票、競選，將台灣與香港的狀況進行對比，引發熱議。港星杜汶澤今也在臉書貼出一段45秒的影片，他在影片中表示自己是個沒有投票權的香港人，呼籲台灣民眾1月11日一定要記得去投票，守護得來不易的民主自由。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/awJ4zGZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FawJ4zGZ.jpg&h=5e7253c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲杜汶澤在臉書呼籲台灣民眾一定要記得去投票。（圖／翻攝自臉書）<br />\n<br />\n杜汶澤今在臉書貼出一段45秒的影片，他寫道「親愛的台灣，你知道你幸福嗎？」，「民主，對於台灣人來說，能夠擁有是基本權利，就像空氣一樣。但對於香港人來說，就算是血流披面，民主，也是遙不可及」。影片搭配香港反送中運動的街頭實景，許多學生被港警打到頭破血流，令人怵目驚心。<br />\n<br />\n杜汶澤在影片中沉痛呼籲民眾一定要記得去投票，守護得來不易的民主自由，「我是杜汶澤，一個沒有投票權的香港人，請大家珍惜自己的權利，1月11號，回家投票」，短短45秒的影片簡潔有力、震撼人心，成功引發網友討論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/karma.dawa.7/videos/1769620383171868/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkarma.dawa.7%2Fvideos%2F1769620383171868%2F&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF0wpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=bad56015\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/karma.dawa.7/videos/1769620383171868/</a>"},{"pid":"080d06e9417b21f9a40a3d8f1d49d84ed8637a2e","tid":1817412,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:23:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=668850\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D668850&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF0wpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=f8051e36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D668850&h=09a4139f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=668850</a>"},{"pid":"ab712c2f52b662b9a175a0546da71bb8c7e6b25f","tid":1817412,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:24:12.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[全港最大的Fact Check平台-非食店篇]集合超過400間各地區各行業的良心店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1817378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1817378</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c8c75e60f17bd7213edb58c9e603588a86de4960","tid":1817412,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T05:32:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5sLiuwxlfTE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5sLiuwxlfTE&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF0wpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=ba5a6f30\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5sLiuwxlfTE</a><br />\n湯德章歷史實境劇&mdash;2019年台南實境演出！"}]}